{"tid":807343,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"數碼通真係電訊界清泉！","createTime":"2018-09-05T12:08:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-12T03:45:22.000Z","uid":64767,"like":1,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"9366e8b8b810d8d5d11eaffe277729ed6a77b805","tid":807343,"uid":64767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T12:08:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.eprice.com.hk/mobile/talk/3149/211332/1/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.eprice.com.hk%2Fmobile%2Ftalk%2F3149%2F211332%2F1%2F&d=MWJ%2FoQsH6fUX2op4UrBM2pWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=15bab276\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.eprice.com.hk/mobile/talk/3149/211332/1/</a><br />\n<br />\n睇左呢篇news先，數記係第一間電訊商暫時用LAA，最快去到1Gbps而且實行緊既<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過呢啲唔撚係重點，重點係以我所知其他電訊商之後都會出，但佢地係用黎連接4G/5G頻譜既設備全部都係強國華為，而數碼通就用歐洲嘢愛立信！ <br />\n<br />\n呀屌乜而家啲電訊商咁愛國架咩？咁愛國返大陸上網就唔撚洗漫游啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然暫時得Sony XZ2 Premium 支援LAA網絡，但相信黎緊新機如iPhone都會支援LAA，同埋其他An旗艦機都會支援!<br />\n <br />\n一句講哂數碼通係電訊界清泉，不服來辯 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3c1a421b1326044d1ba2ada3dc1817b565dc976","tid":807343,"uid":89931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-05T13:21:11.000Z","msg":"laa係要硬件支援定係軟件就ok？"},{"pid":"a794e9b8e4c86a6093f03a07039cfcdf8c68ec40","tid":807343,"uid":172458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T04:00:52.000Z","msg":"憑一部電話就睇到係清泉?"},{"pid":"a3d19a4b24394b4f5d1fd8b41cc371691ee9e230","tid":807343,"uid":16453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a794e9b8e4c86a6093f03a07039cfcdf8c68ec40","tid":807343,"uid":172458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T04:00:52.000Z","msg":"憑一部電話就睇到係清泉?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-06T04:14:06.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">而數碼通就用歐洲嘢愛立信！</span><br />\n<br />\n文肓?"},{"pid":"158c030c80e81780aacd5bbdc72